# 📌 Overview

PrepAI is a full-stack AI-powered interview preparation platform designed to help students and job seekers prepare for software engineering interviews.

The platform combines mock interviews, resume analysis, DSA tracking, personalized study plans, company-specific roadmaps, analytics, and voice-based interview practice using modern web technologies and free AI models.

---

# ✨ Features

### 🎤 AI Mock Interviews

* AI-generated interview questions
* Voice & text interview modes
* Real-time evaluation
* Per-answer feedback
* Overall interview report
* Performance score

---

### 📄 Resume Analyzer

* Upload resume
* AI-powered resume review
* ATS suggestions
* Skill gap detection
* Improvement recommendations

---

### 📚 Company Roadmaps

Generate interview preparation roadmaps for:

* Amazon
* Google
* Microsoft
* Meta
* Adobe
* Flipkart
* Atlassian
* Uber
* Goldman Sachs
* Walmart Labs
* Infosys
* TCS

---

### 💻 DSA Tracker

Track:

* Solved problems
* Difficulty distribution
* Topic-wise progress
* Daily streak
* Overall statistics

---

### 📅 Personalized Study Plans

Generate week-by-week preparation plans based on:

* Target company
* Available study hours
* Current skill level
* Interview timeline

---

### 📊 Analytics Dashboard

Visualize your progress using charts:

* Interview scores
* DSA completion
* Weekly progress
* Study consistency
* Resume improvements

---

### 🎙️ Voice Mode

Uses the browser's native Web Speech API.

Features:

* Speech Recognition
* AI Question Reading
* Hands-free interview experience

Works best on:

* Google Chrome
* Microsoft Edge

---

### 🔐 Authentication

* JWT Authentication
* Password Hashing (bcrypt)
* Protected Routes
* Persistent Login

---

# 🛠 Tech Stack

## Frontend

* React 18
* Vite
* Tailwind CSS
* Wouter
* TanStack Query
* Axios
* Recharts
* Lucide Icons

## Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MongoDB
* Mongoose

## Authentication

* JWT
* bcryptjs

## AI

Primary

* Groq
* llama-3.3-70b-versatile

Fallback

* Google Gemini 2.0 Flash

