# ⚙️ Installation

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/aditibh19/Prep-Ai.git

cd Prep-Ai
```

---

## Backend Setup

```bash
cd backend

npm install
```

Create `.env`

```env
PORT=5000

MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection

JWT_SECRET=your_secret

GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_key

GEMINI_API_KEY=optional

CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:5173
```

Run backend

```bash
npm run dev
```

---

## Frontend Setup

```bash
cd frontend

npm install

npm run dev
```

Visit

```
http://localhost:5173
```

---

# 🔑 Environment Variables

| Variable       | Required |
| -------------- | -------- |
| MONGO_URI      | ✅        |
| JWT_SECRET     | ✅        |
| GROQ_API_KEY   | ✅        |
| GEMINI_API_KEY | Optional |
| CLIENT_URL     | Optional |
| PORT           | Optional |

