# 🤖 AI Architecture

```
                 User
                   │
                   ▼
           Express Backend
                   │
        ┌──────────┴──────────┐
        │                     │
        ▼                     ▼
      Groq AI           Gemini AI
   (Primary Model)    (Fallback Model)
```

